<br>
I was PKed and corpse camped back when my Necro was level 26ish for a couple hours by a level 20 gnome rogue that has his epic. Those who are unfamiliar with this tactic: Rogue in uber guild gets his epic. Then levels like normal till high 50's or low 60's. Gets bored of his life and makes a new main so he can turn his Rogue into a &quot;PK grief machine&quot;.<br>
<br>
He gets a bind in WFP next to the gate guards (or any other place good for &quot;respawn suicide&quot;. Punches them and dies, zones back in, punches again. Repeats this until he is level 20. Goes to Paludal with his uber offense and defense skill of  200ish each, puts on his fungi tunic, catches everyone because he has Innate Run Speed 3, beats the shit out of everyone and thier mom with his epic (and blinding poisons) and is completely immune to other players because he is a demi-god.<br>
<br>
