<br>
Bards, Rangers, Shadowknights, Beastlords, Magicians, Necromancers, Druids, and sometimes Wizards and Rogues are all really fun and effective PK classes.<br>
<br>
TZ server is a +8, -8 level PK server. Meaning I can attack someone of an apposing &quot;racial team&quot; 8 levels over me or under me. (This means a level 65 SK can't walk into Freeport and HT a newb to death just because he had a bad day).<br>
A kill = loot all coins he was carrying and his dignity. You cannot attack someone until they have reached level 6 (this is so a level 9 won't prey upon level 1's and kill them with one swing.) Also, you can't have your money looted until you are level 10. You do not lose exp by being slain by a player but your manabar will be empty when you arrive at your bind point.<br>
<br>
 I also like PVP because its the only place where i'm able to tell people what I think about them and not get reported for language. I have done alot of bad shit so far and nobody cared to report me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  As a rule, I generally never report someone harassing me either unless they did something really fucked up.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Here are the teams:</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
#1) Shorts: Halfling, Gnome, Dwarf<br>
#2) Elves: Woodelf, Hielf, Halfelf<br>
#3) Humans: Erudite, Human, Barbarian, Vah Shir, Froglok<br>
#4) Evils: Iksar, Darkelf, Troll, Ogre<br>
<br>
I'm currently working on a Vah Shir Bard griefer ATM that i'm going to whip out and own people with when they bug the shit out of my main. Its funny when Necros snare and dot me and I play my cancel magic song and remove it all while running out of his spell range. Its also good to mez thier pet so they have shittier DPS. I like to keep thier pets mezzed and run around playing cancel magic to keep thier dots from sticking to me very long till they get low on mana from wasting time with me then my friends that were hiding in the zone rush him on my signal and slay and split the plat and make fun of him and his guild and toss around a couple insults. (Something that would be frowned upon on Rathe).<br>
<br>
I have a level 20 Darkelf Mage that never gets any exp. I keep him 20th because thats a nice benchmark of where the good spells for his level are and I use him to purposly hunt and slay people around level 12. I usually pick on Rogues (because I can see invis and he can't click hide and sneak off on me) and my Earth pet keeps him rooted while I lay into him with nukes (pet has on my fire DS on in case Rogue tries to poke him). Wizards are fun to pick on too because at level 20 my nuke is about as good as thiers except I have a pet to keep him interrupted and punch him while I nuke him down. <br>
<br>
My funniest kill was a Warrior that just brought down a HG and was wounded badly trying to bandage up. I ran up to him while invis with my Necro and tossed a Venom of the Snake dot on him then shadowstepped and invised up then ran back over to him to watch him quickly trying to bandage up while the dot was eating him. The dot wore off and he had a little HPs left so I tossed another VoS on him and he shouted &quot;GOD FUCK YOU GOD FUCK DAMN YOU FUCKING NECROS&quot;. He dropped dead soon and I looted him and made about 500 plat! He must have been hunting them for at least an hour. I was amazed that I got that rich in 3 minutes of work from fucking with a human warrior.<br>
<br>
I gave a tell to him asking him what I should buy with his money. His reply wasn't very nice, it had to do with my mom. I then decided to prey upon HG farmers and make off with thier plat to build up my bank on this server. I'm going to make a ton of pp a day doing this (except those Druids that port out every 200 pp and dump it in PoK bank then gate back to RM) <br>
<br>
If you had the patience to read through all of this and you still want to struggle in a REALLY deadly world, you should try Tallon Zek or Vallon Zek when you want a little break from Rathe. When you log back into the Rathe, everyone will seem so much more polite and helpful than you ever realized before <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
